1
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:53,030
General, it is indeed a sandstorm.

2
00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:54,500
We can't travel in this condition.

3
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:56,160
Circling the horses and tying them up is the best plan.

4
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:56,630
Okay.

5
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:01,630
Since we're not taking her with us,

6
00:01:01,630 --> 00:01:02,430
why save her?

7
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:05,330
Saving people is the duty of our soldiers.

8
00:01:05,530 --> 00:01:07,530
So are we going to save her this time?

9
00:01:07,630 --> 00:01:08,230
If we can't save one person,

10
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:09,330
how can we save the country?

11
00:01:09,330 --> 00:01:10,030
If we ignore one person,

12
00:01:10,030 --> 00:01:11,560
how can we protect our land?

13
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,300
Looking at her clothes,

14
00:01:13,300 --> 00:01:14,400
she should be a citizen of Dasheng.

15
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,760
And she's being chased by Canglang soldiers.

16
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,890
So what do you think?

17
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,430
You are the general,

18
00:01:18,430 --> 00:01:19,460
you can't afford to be in danger.

19
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:20,900
If anyone saves her, it should be me.

20
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:23,830
You forgot my horse Feilu can protect its master.

21
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:25,860
You'll just add to the risk if you go.

22
00:01:27,300 --> 00:01:29,800
Listen to my order. I leave this to you.

23
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:31,060
If I can't return,

24
00:01:31,060 --> 00:01:32,060
don't look for me.

25
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:33,259
Keep moving.

26
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,300
Hold the reins tight.

27
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:48,060
Don't panic.

28
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:06,660
Feilu, hurry up! It's urgent!

29
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,560
Help!

30
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,060
Get behind me!

31
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:16,000
Don't be afraid. It will pass soon.

32
00:04:06,130 --> 00:04:08,860
Damn it, I was scared out of my wits.

33
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,260
Death is death.

34
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:12,860
I'm willing to die in battle.

35
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,130
If I die here,

36
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:15,660
wouldn't it be for nothing?

37
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,529
Let go. Don't hug my neck.

38
00:04:19,730 --> 00:04:20,959
I won't.

39
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:25,690
If you don't, you sit in the front.

40
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:31,260
Okay, but if I sit in the front, you'll be hugging me.

41
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,120
Who do you miss the most right now?

42
00:04:33,130 --> 00:04:34,030
My mom.

43
00:04:34,659 --> 00:04:35,860
Besides your mom?

44
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:37,300
My dad.

45
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,900
Don't you miss women?

46
00:04:40,659 --> 00:04:41,860
My mom taught me that

47
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:43,260
if a soldier misses women,

48
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,460
he can't be a general.

49
00:04:45,659 --> 00:04:47,159
You should just take me in.

50
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:49,030
That way my conscience will be clear.

51
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:51,490
Otherwise, I can only repay you with my life.

52
00:04:52,330 --> 00:04:54,130
Do you want me to leave you here?

53
00:04:54,530 --> 00:04:55,530
Looking at your outfit,

54
00:04:55,530 --> 00:04:57,560
are you a general of the Dasheng army?

55
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,330
Yes.

56
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,160
Are you heading towards

57
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,020
General Tie Xiangquan's troops?

58
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,800
You exposed your whereabouts when you saved me last time.

59
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,760
I'll lead you to avoid the Canglang rangers.

60
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,890
Who exactly are you?

61
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:11,100
I was the daughter of a tribe leader.

62
00:05:11,230 --> 00:05:13,560
Canglang King Ashina unified Mobei

63
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,090
and killed my whole family.

64
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:17,230
Find a place and live well.

65
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:18,400
Don't think about revenge.

66
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,400
I will avenge you.

67
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:25,620
I'll leave this horse and the water on it for you.

68
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:28,600
This woman is really lucky.

69
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:33,000
Unload all unnecessary baggage.

70
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,000
Hide the bows, rations, and water.

71
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,530
Only bring one set of flint.

72
00:05:35,659 --> 00:05:36,530
Keep the light armor.

73
00:05:36,530 --> 00:05:37,159
Discard heavy armor components

74
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:38,600
and extra weapons right here.

75
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,260
General,

76
00:05:39,460 --> 00:05:41,960
we still need to cross the wilderness to reach General Tie's camp.

77
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,330
Without enough weapons and supplies,

78
00:05:43,330 --> 00:05:44,659
what if we encounter the outriders of the Canglang Empire?

79
00:05:44,659 --> 00:05:46,100
If carrying these burdens

80
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:46,960
delays us

81
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,030
and causes the main camp to fall,

82
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:49,600
that would be our true doom.

83
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:50,600
Our lives right now

84
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,900
don't depend on how thick our armor is

85
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:53,100
or how many arrows we have,

86
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,760
but on our saddles and hooves.

87
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:08,800
Report, our rations and supplies have been burned again.

88
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:11,600
Halt the attack.

89
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:13,730
Go back and make camp.

90
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,430
Retreat.

91
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,200
Retreat.

92
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:18,660
Retreat.

93
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,860
The enemy's attack is weakening now,

94
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,700
which means Chen Gan succeeded.

95
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:32,330
Let everyone rest if they can.

96
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,700
Let's go out and welcome him.

97
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,260
Sir, are you sure he will run?

98
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,300
According to your plan,

99
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:56,330
near the shortcut heading southwest to the Canglang camp,

100
00:06:56,330 --> 00:06:58,330
our men have let their guard down.

101
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,500
Sigh, I thought about it carefully.

102
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,730
History must have changed.

103
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,400
Gu Shanhe's entire family was executed because he was falsely accused of treason.

104
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,500
The informant is very likely Wang Huiyue.

105
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,660
Good work, everyone.

106
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:12,260
Good work, Army Supervisor.

107
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,200
Hahaha.

108
00:07:13,930 --> 00:07:15,400
Although the enemy has temporarily retreated,

109
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:17,460
we cannot slack off in these unusual times.

110
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:18,930
Bring me a horse.

111
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:19,660
I want to patrol the camp.

112
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:21,930
Right, did you give the item to Chen Gan?

113
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,130
I did. As you instructed,

114
00:07:25,130 --> 00:07:27,190
I told him to read it after the battle.

115
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,730
I figured that

116
00:07:30,330 --> 00:07:32,530
as long as Chen Gan burns their rations again,

117
00:07:32,530 --> 00:07:34,260
they will definitely retreat.

118
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:37,130
Then they will surely bypass Xiangshi Mountain to the rear of our camp

119
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,400
to surround our army.

120
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:43,130
So this move is crucial.

121
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:46,260
After successfully sneaking up on the enemy's rear rations,

122
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:49,200
lead the remnants quickly to the old path of Xiangshi Mountain.

123
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,430
If you encounter the enemy passing by

124
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,260
to attack the rear of the main camp.

125
00:07:52,260 --> 00:07:53,630
There is no need to engage.

126
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:55,260
Just wave the flags, shout,

127
00:07:55,260 --> 00:07:56,430
and light fires to make smoke.

128
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:58,630
To create the illusion of thousands of ambushing soldiers.

129
00:07:58,630 --> 00:08:00,800
The God of Fire just won a battle.

130
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,660
We are not livestock.

131
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:03,400
Shouldn't we be allowed to rest?

132
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,830
Fighting non-stop like this

133
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,090
is exhausting as hell.

134
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:08,430
Think about your parents and your wife.

135
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:10,360
Then you won't be tired.

136
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,760
My parents are long gone,

137
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:14,720
and I certainly don't have a wife.

138
00:08:15,330 --> 00:08:17,390
You'll have one when this war is over.

139
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,430
Arrest him.

140
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,030
Wait.

141
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,260
I am Wang Huiyue, the Army Supervisor of Dasheng.

142
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:33,200
I'm on your side.

143
00:08:33,929 --> 00:08:35,730
The Army Supervisor of Dasheng?

144
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:38,799
How can you prove you're on our side?

145
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,490
This is a top military secret.

146
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:52,160
Don't tell me you want to see it too?

147
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:52,930
Just give it to me.
